java.lang.Object
test.Phase1AutomatedTests.UsernameValidationTests
Enclosing class:
Phase1AutomatedTests
@Nested @DisplayName("Username Validation Tests") public class Phase1AutomatedTests.UsernameValidationTests extends Object
Test suite for username validation. Tests various aspects of username requirements including: - Length constraints (4-16 characters) - Character type restrictions - Special character placement rules
Version:
1.00 2025-04-01 Initial implementation of all validation test suites
